headline.main: Dr. W. Henry Sebrell, 91, Expert On Nutrition and Use of Vitamins

docs.lead_paragraph: W. Henry Sebrell Jr., a pioneer in vitamin research and an international authority on nutrition, died yesterday at his home in Pompano Beach, Fla. He was 91 years old. He died of cancer, his family said.
